&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMPORTANT: This role is only available to those 13+ years of age and residents of the United States or Canada.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is a waitlist. The next cohort will launch in September 2026.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;---&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kiva has launched an Ambassador Community, and we’re inviting you to build it with us! &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Together, we can open even more doors to financial opportunity through word of mouth and community building.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;As a Kiva Ambassador, you&#39;d be Kiva&#39;s voice for financial inclusion, and you’ll impact even more lives. Every new person you introduce to Kiva can mean an entrepreneur funded, a child educated, a family flourishing, and a community transformed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Your personal stories and experiences are far more powerful than any advertisement we could come up with. Since 2005, word of mouth has been our most effective way to grow our community of lenders. According to a recent lender survey, over 40% of lenders who tried Kiva for the first time heard about us from a friend or family member. Kiva advocates are making a tremendous impact!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You’ve likely already shared Kiva with your family and friends. Now, imagine extending that reach even further. Curious about what being a Kiva Ambassador entails? Check out the role and apply below.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;-----&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We ask Kiva Ambassadors to volunteer about 2 hours per week (for 6 months) supporting Kiva in reaching new audiences and lenders.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What do Kiva Ambassadors do?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Start a &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.kiva.org/lp/giving-fund&quot;&gt;Kiva giving fund&lt;/a&gt; and share it with your family, friends, and more.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You could...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share Kiva&#39;s mission with clubs, community associations, places of worship, and other groups&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Host a birthday fundraiser for Kiva&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Start a Kiva club&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;…do almost anything you can think of to share Kiva with your network&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For Ambassadors, Kiva will...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide access to an exclusive community where you can connect, share ideas, and learn from one another&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Connect you with Kiva leadership team and CEO&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide you with opportunities to learn about financial inclusion and social impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide you with resources needed to share Kiva&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Recognize you with special events, swag, and more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A least 13 years of age. (Participation by those under 18 will require a guardian or parent&#39;s permission)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reside and promote Kiva within the United States or Canada&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that this is an unpaid &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/document/d/19U-NkjStrG7aZyUfpQ_AyyvacDRbOCG_/edit&quot;&gt;volunteer role&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

